Asmi gemmut Stifan, yekker uqehheṛ i gessemfaṛaqen inelmaden ɣer mkul amkan ; ṛuḥen armi ț-țamurt n Krijya, armi ț-țigzirt n Qubṛus ț-țemdint n wat Isṛail.
Akken daɣen i d-țbanen lecɣal lɛali, ma d lecɣal n diri ur zmiren ara ad qqimen ffren.
Ini-yi-d daɣen i wedɣaɣal n temdint n Luier, n Biririn, d izumal ara zwiǧen deg iberdan n lewqam n lebḥeṛ, neɣ ț-țigzirt i d-ițeddun ɣer temdint n Dundu.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa dwalt-nni, ifkan iberdan n lewqat akk-d lḥut s țțawil.
Seg wass-nni, yiwen umeḥbus mechuṛen di Lmasiḥ, ițțusemman « Tafaska n izimer n leslak » tqeṛb-ed.
Aṭas n tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, di tejmaɛt n wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ akk-d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, ma d win ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ ara yilin di ddunit-agi,
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ; dɣa iwala-t di beṛṛa mbla lxedma.
Deg ussan-nni, llan seg wat Isṛail i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, ițbeggin-ed s yiman-nsen ad xedmen lbeṛhanat d ussexṛeb, lameɛna ilaq aț-țilim di leɛwayed n yemdanen di temdint n Lquds akk-d ț-țilawin.
Aṭas n watmaten mkul ass i deg ilaq ad ițțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi. Mi d-yewweḍ wass n westeɛfu, aṭas n wat Isṛail i d-innejmaɛen seg weqṛaḥ n ccṛeɛ ; ma d tejmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yeqqim si yiḍ, i ț-id-iwɛed ɣef ḥeggu n Lmasiḥ.
Timsalin-agi akk i sen-yedṛan, qqiment-ed d lemtel, uran-tent di tektabin, iwakken a nelmed nukni ițɛicin di taggara n lweqt.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Lquds, daymi i s-ițwaceggɛen ayen ur neṣfi ara, axaṭer ṭṭfet di lbabuṛ ur zmiren ara ad iṛuḥ ula d aɣebbaṛ n warkafriwen-nsen.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i waḍu n tmurt n Galasya : imezṛaǧen, i yeqjan, ikeṛṛusen akk-d wid yeznuzun, igduden, lɣaci n Sidna Ɛisa akk-d weqṛaḥ, iɛewjen taɛeṣṣabt.
M'ara d-taseḍ, aqcic-nni ara d-yewḍen si cceṛq seg umalu, ara d-yuɣalen si lexla. Imeslayen-agi, ur yezmir ara a d-isbeggen i wid i d-yekkan si wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ.
Llan deg-s lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen n mkul yiwen seg-sen, axaṭer kra yemdanen yeṭṭfen deg-sen ur d-yețțak ara tafat. Acḥal yelha m'ara nwali teddun deg igenwan, yethedden wul-nsen ad iqdec.
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan leḥkumat n tejmaɛt n Yahuda yellan di tmurt-agi, aṭas ara iɛicen s lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen, yerna ad yili win ara d-yesfehmen ayen i d-qqaṛen :
Tebṛeq, terfaḍ ț-țadliwin s ufus n wemdan, ma d wiyaḍ, ad xedmen ccɣel i sen-d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i tilas n ccɣel-nneɣ.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓiyen i wid meṛṛa, ilaq a d-cehden fell-as ad lemden zdat medden meṛṛa.
